  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一张Mir合成器架构的类图，核心是展示Compositor怎么把miral和mirwayland这两部分整合起来。miral是主API层，mirwayland是扩展API层，它们都依赖底层的mircore。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Compositor",
        "miral",
        "mirwayland",
        "mircore"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。让我确认一下关系方向：miral和mirwayland各自独立依赖mircore，然后Compositor同时聚合了miral和mirwayland，对吗？不需要画Compositor到mircore的直接连线？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "miral",
        "mirwayland",
        "mircore",
        "Compositor"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Compositor不直接碰mircore，它通过miral和mirwayland来间接使用。miral提供窗口管理这些主API，mirwayland专门处理Wayland协议扩展。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Compositor",
        "miral",
        "mirwayland",
        "mircore"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出四个类节点，把miral和mirwayland的别名标注上，然后建立那四条依赖和聚合关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "miral",
        "mirwayland",
        "mircore",
        "Compositor"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，miral的别名写反了，应该是\"miral (main APIs)\"，不是\"miral (Extension APIs)\"。另外mirwayland的别名也要对应改成\"mirwayland (Extension APIs)\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "miral",
        "mirwayland"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修正，现在miral标注为main APIs，mirwayland标注为Extension APIs。四条关系线也确认无误：miral--mircore、mirwayland--mircore、Compositor--miral、Compositor--mirwayland。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "miral",
        "mirwayland",
        "mircore",
        "Compositor"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "这个结构能体现出tension关系吗？就是Compositor要同时协调miral的传统窗口管理和mirwayland的Wayland扩展，有时候会有设计张力。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Compositor",
        "miral",
        "mirwayland",
        "tension"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "目前的连线已经暗示了这种tension——Compositor同时拉两条线，一条到miral一条到mirwayland，视觉上能看出它需要平衡两边。如果需要显式标注，我们可以加注释，但当前类图保持简洁可能更好？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Compositor",
        "miral",
        "mirwayland",
        "tension"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
